","tid":756350,"uid":149961,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:12:09.000Z","msg":"之前朋友隻狗都係咁<br />\n直至有日帶左佢去睇獸醫先知佢d牙有問題而d糧太硬所以先會自給自足"},{"pid":"8dc7dca65bb19c8cce2572082b9be9a931f810d6","tid":756350,"uid":51387,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6ab80c3ffeb68bc8af78c5b9a7718f15b643d774","tid":756350,"uid":90638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T03:33:21.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我係親戚個到領養左隻哥基bb<br />\n但係佢開始有食屎嘅習慣<br />\n到底我應該做咩先可阻止到佢？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/26/113316_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F113316_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2ab74ce9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:12:31.000Z","msg":"見佢食一次就打一次得唔得?"},{"pid":"d936025918077f3dbcbfa0460f19560af2772d69","tid":756350,"uid":95667,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:13:04.000Z","msg":"我隻貴婦到3歲都會食返自己啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eac5d67358afa308c8e32d4fda3d65bd982c6ca","tid":756350,"uid":121710,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:14:10.000Z","msg":"得一張圖點答"},{"pid":"cb36a40fa6cc2abad3dc8a96a5f1b8044fd31c42","tid":756350,"uid":31003,"like":146,"dislike":5,"score":141,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:14:19.000Z","msg":"上面果d好撚低質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n又唔係好笑就收皮啦<br />\n<br />\n狗狗食屎係因為d便便有食物氣味殘留<br />\n樓主你試下係佢痾完你加檸檬汁落佢d便便<br />\n等佢中一次招應該就唔會再食<br />\n除非你又轉糧<br />\n<br />\n唔得就要用第2個方法 試試行為訓練<br />\n當佢行埋去聞屎或食屎 你就搵水槍仔射佢<br />\n唔好俾佢發現係你射佢<br />\n久而久之佢就知食屎係會整濕自己 佢就唔會食<br />\n<br />\n注意如果佢知係你射佢 佢只會唔係你面前食<br />\n所以先叫你用水槍仔 遠距離神不知鬼不覺<br />\n<br />\n唔好試用打或者鬧 有d狗會更加反抗 搶屎食睇性格"},{"pid":"0ab9a32c92efaa3ea4e5c952e7fae6ffc5712a70","tid":756350,"uid":172643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:15:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f761cf28ef14b95fb6bd45403b4f6047b65b2847","tid":756350,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:15:40.000Z","msg":"鍚佢嘴仔叫佢唔好`食"},{"pid":"b28fbbcf914a440dde916aa6226ec4d98443acde","tid":756350,"uid":108738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"385e96c0488474b7e130d4e416368468eed79f2e","tid":756350,"uid":158907,"like":34,"dislike":3,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T03:54:11.000Z","msg":"食屎 有機會係隻糧唔啱 轉糧就得<br />\n亦都有機會係狗狗條腸唔夠益生菌 去寵物店買益生菌比隻狗狗食 消化好左就唔會食屎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:17:29.000Z","msg":"正解<br />\n<br />\n但如果以上方法都唔得，就係冇解，你唯有盡快執等佢冇機會食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 屋企有隻狗都食"},{"pid":"a6f9bf10eb936de05c456904393c320f3a257dc9","tid":756350,"uid":4739,"like":55,"dislike":2,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:17:35.000Z","msg":"其實寵物既學習能力好高<br />\n隻狗仔仲細應該慢慢教就ok<br />\n下次見佢食屎可以話下佢<br />\n同埋平時比飽d佢食<br />\n比著係你飽左都唔會搵屎食啦<br />\n加上清多d砂盤，唔好比佢有臭臭樓低<br />\n咁自然佢想食都冇得食啦<br />\n當然，最重要都係樓主以身作則<br />\n下次係狗仔面前就唔好食喇<br />\n動物既學習能力好高，你話係咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"750c0e5df2bc25b97b15b2f8e8d1df80c9c7105e","tid":756350,"uid":153400,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:20:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/b/b4/DcewtdN.gif/revision/latest?cb=20140127163846\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fb%2Fb4%2FDcewtdN.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20140127163846&h=ef8265ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bab6340b53182506023b95e47f15248b01892f08","tid":756350,"uid":84367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:24:53.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"ca46dce5241d332f7ab03d1c4f649b648e861b99","tid":756350,"uid":13116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:26:06.000Z","msg":"比多D好野佢食<br />\n佢就知食屎是無味"},{"pid":"09e13600815e19eeec4f9ab7ce25e7824017ab4f","tid":756350,"uid":92656,"like":16,"dislike":6,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:28:21.000Z","msg":"child登小學雞真係好撚白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成班見到食屎兩隻字即刻覺得好好玩好好笑<br />\n喺度貼埋哂咩食屎狗，完全唔理樓主係認真問野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a380f81ad6fe010c090c188586dfdbcd2d3e8fa9","tid":756350,"uid":41302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:28:36.000Z","msg":"d糧佢消化唔曬 殘留左狗糧既味道係屎<br />\n換一隻岩佢既糧 （全部都係聽人講）"},{"pid":"751e3c29aa11e1890cbbea60077d3e0d5132fe2c","tid":756350,"uid":44884,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:33:37.000Z","msg":"好可愛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b554ab04c2f9be20a9b83dc98d9ad2dd7818151e","tid":756350,"uid":151717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cb36a40fa6cc2abad3dc8a96a5f1b8044fd31c42","tid":756350,"uid":31003,"like":146,"dislike":5,"score":141,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:14:19.000Z","msg":"上面果d好撚低質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n又唔係好笑就收皮啦<br />\n<br />\n狗狗食屎係因為d便便有食物氣味殘留<br />\n樓主你試下係佢痾完你加檸檬汁落佢d便便<br />\n等佢中一次招應該就唔會再食<br />\n除非你又轉糧<br />\n<br />\n唔得就要用第2個方法 試試行為訓練<br />\n當佢行埋去聞屎或食屎 你就搵水槍仔射佢<br />\n唔好俾佢發現係你射佢<br />\n久而久之佢就知食屎係會整濕自己 佢就唔會食<br />\n<br />\n注意如果佢知係你射佢 佢只會唔係你面前食<br />\n所以先叫你用水槍仔 遠距離神不知鬼不覺<br />\n<br />\n唔好試用打或者鬧 有d狗會更加反抗 搶屎食睇性格"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:36:52.000Z","msg":"水槍仔調教小哥基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗到支水槍射哥基個patpat就想玩玩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2656441393d44c6c332c5eb3c71b73de3e315ab8","tid":756350,"uid":37389,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:38:37.000Z","msg":"狗呢，係食屎嘅，好正常，除咗人類覺得好核突，對佢地健康其實無影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而幼犬比成犬更常食<br />\n<br />\n通常就兩個原因，一係吸引你注意，一係就隻狗糧味道重，幼犬消化系統未成熟，痾出黎啲屎有陣糧味，佢地就會食返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以解決方法得兩個：快過佢食屎執屎，同埋換糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n養咗狗好耐，見怪不怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86dab473b611ce3e7c97c23f796d24983906727","tid":756350,"uid":111002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:39:56.000Z","msg":"狗食屎有機會係屎入面有食物味道，最常見係動物收容中心果D狗，佢地無野做，又肚餓就會走去食。<br />\n<br />\n處理方法主要係勤力D清走佢大便，如果見到佢食就阻止佢食同鬧佢，係教狗嘅一部分，趁佢重係細個，順便教佢咩唔做得<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">利申：返左幾日SSA實SAA狗場，頂唔住辭左</span></span>"},{"pid":"fc30297e27aaaa0832b87d694ce2f441e9c55c2e","tid":756350,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:43:06.000Z","msg":"大嘅唔好教壞細"},{"pid":"8a9d83ca1922b23f4083aa8a5ec28b4b05939367","tid":756350,"uid":31323,"like":6,"dislike":16,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"cb36a40fa6cc2abad3dc8a96a5f1b8044fd31c42","tid":756350,"uid":31003,"like":146,"dislike":5,"score":141,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:14:19.000Z","msg":"上面果d好撚低質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n又唔係好笑就收皮啦<br />\n<br />\n狗狗食屎係因為d便便有食物氣味殘留<br />\n樓主你試下係佢痾完你加檸檬汁落佢d便便<br />\n等佢中一次招應該就唔會再食<br />\n除非你又轉糧<br />\n<br />\n唔得就要用第2個方法 試試行為訓練<br />\n當佢行埋去聞屎或食屎 你就搵水槍仔射佢<br />\n唔好俾佢發現係你射佢<br />\n久而久之佢就知食屎係會整濕自己 佢就唔會食<br />\n<br />\n注意如果佢知係你射佢 佢只會唔係你面前食<br />\n所以先叫你用水槍仔 遠距離神不知鬼不覺<br />\n<br />\n唔好試用打或者鬧 有d狗會更加反抗 搶屎食睇性格"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:43:33.000Z","msg":"幾歲人啊 仲係咁打疊字<br />\n睇到打撚晒冷震 <br />\n屎就屎啦 便你老味便咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b91d78ac5ae5be91d0adbc20cbd1f9945c8f02","tid":756350,"uid":188624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:49:50.000Z","msg":"我個隻四歲半都仲食緊<br />\n一係貪玩<br />\n二係啲屎仲有食物嘅氣味<br />\n三係想引你注意"},{"pid":"11726ca5c0d8de7d77a336e5889b19a98a579675","tid":756350,"uid":73968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:50:08.000Z","msg":"滴白花油落屎到"},{"pid":"ab56ea2ed109877890d2d1cc14e0374bed15aac0","tid":756350,"uid":9711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:50:49.000Z","msg":"係因為狗仔腸胃唔好 有食物未完全消化完 所以會食返<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a46178b454344437981807e17ada098bb39d8e","tid":756350,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:51:50.000Z","msg":"永動機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cdf77e236531c5c80292ea8ab7c56cb67bc5c10","tid":756350,"uid":45693,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:52:29.000Z","msg":"有聽過狗狗係缺乏安全感先會食返自己啲屎屎<br />\n野生動物屙完屎會踢啲沙呀泥呀去遮蔽返自己嘅行跡，驚比其他動物追蹤到浸味"},{"pid":"6dfcae98fe99b5d5f721dcac409d19ccf79501b8","tid":756350,"uid":165772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:52:42.000Z","msg":"戴口罩"},{"pid":"437ee495466c5dfd07bae8be245775680e6573a3","tid":756350,"uid":8304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:54:05.000Z","msg":"食屎狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我要你連屎都冇得食～～～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43d527ea859c959d1629c86b21b81d6467eb83de","tid":756350,"uid":107835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:57:45.000Z","msg":"我個隻細個都食屎<br />\n成日番到屋企地下有屎漬，但係舊屎就唔知去左邊<br />\n我個時問過朋友，有機會係d糧太大味，佢細個以為係食得，同埋捉到佢食屎記住狠狠地鬧佢，隻哥基大大下就唔會食"},{"pid":"1d5db0385e720da5fce7c5d2d8ba3d686bc5dabb","tid":756350,"uid":97420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:57:50.000Z","msg":"食少少菠蘿<br />\n咁佢啲排泄物就會有一浸佢哋唔鍾意嘅味"},{"pid":"46ec17d50f536c7356643fe7ad8ca7b945b57940","tid":756350,"uid":8748,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T11:08:37.000Z","msg":"睇咗三頁都冇人叫<br />\n<br />\nmore圖 plz<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddcac54c250ae89ef17bdc9b737433801a8333ca","tid":756350,"uid":103346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T11:19:01.000Z","msg":"我個隻開頭半年都會<br />\n不過之後就少左好多"},{"pid":"b2a120e29f3c664868ed323051418e33214d6214","tid":756350,"uid":17718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T11:19:10.000Z","msg":"可以買消化酵素比佢食"},{"pid":"53281944faffa584a7d3b80c5f4a4872fe135ef4","tid":756350,"uid":174017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T11:28:34.000Z","msg":"Bb狗消化系統未成熟 屎屎仲有殘留食物味度所以狗狗以為係食物。<br />\n一係教佢唔食得<br />\n一係就唯有佢一屙完你就即時執屎"},{"pid":"e5e706f63bef3429e05c990665a2b65e41ddd250","tid":756350,"uid":84159,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T11:35:10.000Z","msg":"你個飲水器唔岩狗用 轉返用鐵兜啦 你自己飲水都唔想一滴一滴咁飲啦"},{"pid":"db0d4f666057fdd2da87f0a66086add6452b23b6","tid":756350,"uid":180402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T11:41:12.000Z","msg":"有冇多d相<br />\n好得意呀"},{"pid":"545af8be66fe9c9e762405308d11593b5deeb6f0","tid":756350,"uid":90638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb36a40fa6cc2abad3dc8a96a5f1b8044fd31c42","tid":756350,"uid":31003,"like":146,"dislike":5,"score":141,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:14:19.000Z","msg":"上面果d好撚低質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n又唔係好笑就收皮啦<br />\n<br />\n狗狗食屎係因為d便便有食物氣味殘留<br />\n樓主你試下係佢痾完你加檸檬汁落佢d便便<br />\n等佢中一次招應該就唔會再食<br />\n除非你又轉糧<br />\n<br />\n唔得就要用第2個方法 試試行為訓練<br />\n當佢行埋去聞屎或食屎 你就搵水槍仔射佢<br />\n唔好俾佢發現係你射佢<br />\n久而久之佢就知食屎係會整濕自己 佢就唔會食<br />\n<br />\n注意如果佢知係你射佢 佢只會唔係你面前食<br />\n所以先叫你用水槍仔 遠距離神不知鬼不覺<br />\n<br />\n唔好試用打或者鬧 有d狗會更加反抗 搶屎食睇性格"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T11:42:15.000Z","msg":"thank you<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b3de5ea5bcccbbc117f3c4a05486b7449307472","tid":756350,"uid":88689,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T11:56:16.000Z","msg":"通常係因為食物味<br />\n另外就係愛干淨<br />\n<br />\n要教 要鬧 要打 有獎有罰<br />\n教多幾次就唔會再食<br />\n<br />\n當然打都要識得打 唔可以太暴力<br />\n基本上鬧完佢 佢識驚 驚多幾次就唔敢再做"},{"pid":"3d7153491501a5d2db05b0fe73040c63d154753a","tid":756350,"uid":90638,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"quote":{"pid":"46ec17d50f536c7356643fe7ad8ca7b945b57940","tid":756350,"uid":8748,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T11:08:37.000Z","msg":"睇咗三頁都冇人叫<br />\n<br />\nmore圖 plz<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T11:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/26/195616_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F195616_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4a8ca754&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/26/195618_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F195618_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7a16525d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e10cc7d15656001bf2a8a85dfa828edf6952db3b","tid":756350,"uid":149063,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:07:53.000Z","msg":"試下加小小菠蘿落佢啲食物到<